T ask the user any questions — proceed autonomously.\nDo NOT run git commit. Do NOT run git add. Do NOT modify sprint-status.yaml.","agentId":"a50b4ca183d5022aa","agentType":"general-purpose","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Done. Retrospective appended to `/Users/ivintik/dev/personal/codeharness/_bmad-output/implementation-artifacts/session-retro-2026-03-28.md` with a `---` separator.\n\n**Summary of what was written:**\n\n- **Session 53 (manual)** — no-op session, stale sprint-status.yaml reconciled\n- **Issues analysis** — 1 HIGH, 9 MEDIUM, 8 LOW bugs found by session 52's code review subagents; 8 fixed, 10 deferred as tech debt\n- **Cost analysis** — $898.90 total sprint cost; ~$160-190 (18-21%) estimated waste from no-op Ralph sessions, phantom stories, redundant test runs, and unattributed costs\n- **Subagent breakdown** — 208 tool calls across 12 subagent passes; npm test run ~15 times when 6 would suffice; harness-run.md read 8 times across subagents\n- **Top action items** — stop Ralph (critical), fix state persistence bug, add sprint-complete exit condition, add state reconciliation at session start"}],"totalDurationMs":137130,"totalTokens":36445,"totalToolUseCount":14,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":267,"cache_read_input_tokens":35902,"output_tokens":275,"server_tool_use":{"web_search_requests":0,"web_fetch_requests":0},"service_tier":"standard","cache_creation":{"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":267},"inference_geo":"","iterations":[],"speed":"standard"}}}
